----- Installation -----

Copy the contents of src to a cgi-enabled directory on your web server and access <scriptroot>/"bookmarks.pl" in your browser.

----- Usage ----- 

To add/remove/recategorize bookmarks visit <scriptroot>/"cp.pl".

To add a bookmark from a given page paste the bookmarkelt code
generated on the "cp.pl" page into a bookmark *in your browser*
and use the bookmark to add items to your bookmarks page.

Note: If you are having trouble adding bookmarks, ensure bookmarks.db is writable.

